{"name":"Instructions","_id":"DgIeWGkxkwouUnTW","pages":[{"sort":100000,"name":"Import compendiums (GM)","type":"text","_id":"2LcZpVLxJKPE171o","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>Import all Compendiums, retaining Document IDs. This is important as they are used to link items. For example, the Skills in Professions are stored using the document ID of the Skill.</p>","markdown":""},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1,"NiJh555W408VQRFB":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"brp","systemVersion":"11.0.37","coreVersion":"11.315","createdTime":1702582758843,"modifiedTime":1702583465017,"lastModifiedBy":"NiJh555W408VQRFB"}},{"sort":200000,"name":"Configure Settings (GM)","type":"text","_id":"cKOWCfYuwnm2Jy1b","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>Open the Game Settings &gt; Configure Settings &gt; Basic Role Playing</p><p></p><p><strong>Powers</strong></p><p>Tick the relevant powers that you want to allow in the game. If the box is left unticked you will not be able to add the relevant Power to a character sheet.</p><p></p><p><strong>Optional Rules</strong></p><p>Hits Per Location - tick the box if you want HPL in your game</p><p>Include Education - tick this box to allow characters, NPCs etc to have this optional stat. It will now appear on the character sheet.</p><p>Include Sanity - tick this box to allow characters, NPCs etc to have this optional stat. Sanity Points will now appear on the character sheet.</p><p>Include Fatigue - tick this box to allow characters, NPCs etc to have this optional stat. Fatigue Points will now appear on the character sheet.</p><p>Use Magic Points - tick this box to rename Power Points to Magic Points.</p><p>Skill Bonus - choose from no bonus scores, simple bonus scores or advanced bonus scores</p><p>Use Random Armour Values - this uses random armour values (e.g. 1D6) rather than fixed values (e.g. 2)</p><p></p><p><strong>Customise</strong></p><p>This sections lets you rename the titles for the three background entries available on the character sheet. This will apply to all characters.</p><p></p><p></p>"},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1,"NiJh555W408VQRFB":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"brp","systemVersion":"11.0.37","coreVersion":"11.315","createdTime":1702582868544,"modifiedTime":1702583455351,"lastModifiedBy":"NiJh555W408VQRFB"}},{"sort":300000,"name":"Create a Character","type":"text","_id":"HWU3ZMJR0WSb4q9V","title":{"show":true,"level":1},"image":{},"text":{"format":1,"content":"<p>Create a new actor.  At the moment you can only create Characters</p><p>Enter name, age etc.</p><p>You can drag a Profession and Personality from the items to the character sheet.  Currently it only populates the value, it doesn't apply skill choices (that will come in future development).  Right click on \"Profession\" or \"Personality\" to delete these options.</p><p>Cultures will be added in a future development.</p><p>In the \"Characteristics\" tab enter your stats - these will now show on the front of the character sheet and the \"secondary stats\" values will be calculated.</p><p>Manually input HP, PP, FP and SAN - both current and max values.  Auto-population will come in a future development.</p><p>Include Sanity - tick this box to allow characters, NPCs etc to have this optional stat.  It will now appear on the character sheet.</p><p><strong>Skills Tab</strong></p><p>Drag the relevant skills to the character sheet.  If the character sheet is unlocked (toggle the padlock icon) you can edit the various skill values.  Population of base values etc will be in a future development as will controls around spending skill points.  Locking the character sheets stops the edits but arranges skills by category.  Right clicking the skill name opens a context menu.</p><p><strong>Combat Tab</strong></p><p>Dragging weapons to the character sheet will add them to the weapons section of the Combat tab.  This will automatically add the relevant weapon skill to the skills section if you dont already have it.  The percentage shown is the relevant skill percentage (e.g. Brawling skill for Fist).  Right click the weapon name for a context menu.</p><p>Drag hit locations to the character sheet, again right clicking gives a context menu.  If you don't use Hits Per Location just select the \"Total\" hit location.  Future developments will automatically add these, calculate hit points etc - for now its manual.</p><p><strong>Items Tab</strong></p><p>Drag armour and other equipment to the character sheet to add them.  Right clicking the item name will open up a context menu.</p><p>For equipment there is the \"+\" icon to add items directly to the sheet and the trashcan icon to delete them.</p><p><strong>Magic/Mutation/Psychics/Sorcery/Superpower Tabs</strong></p><p>These tabs will only be visible if you drag the relevant power to the character sheet (and you can only do that if the relevant box is ticked in Game Settings).</p><p>Right clicking the tab name gives you a context menu with an option to delete the power if the character sheet is unlocked.</p><p>Drag the relevant spell, superpower etc to the character sheet to add it.  Right click the spell name, superpower etc for a context menu.</p><p><strong>Characteristics Tab</strong></p><p>As indicated above this is where you enter the actual stats and modifiers.  The options to roll these, controls around min &amp; max values will come in a future development including Cultures.</p><p><strong>Story Tab</strong></p><p>There are three sections where you can enter details about your character.  The section titles are determined in the Game Settings</p>"},"video":{"controls":true,"volume":0.5},"src":null,"system":{},"ownership":{"default":-1,"NiJh555W408VQRFB":3},"flags":{},"_stats":{"systemId":"brp","systemVersion":"11.0.37","coreVersion":"11.315","createdTime":1702585956688,"modifiedTime":1702586888820,"lastModifiedBy":"NiJh555W408VQRFB"}}],"folder":null,"flags":{"core":{}},"_stats":{"systemId":"brp","systemVersion":"11.0.37","coreVersion":"11.315","createdTime":1702582737040,"modifiedTime":1702587344805,"lastModifiedBy":"NiJh555W408VQRFB"},"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"NiJh555W408VQRFB":3}}
